{"meta": {"centerNodeId": "taxonomy-species-terpsiphone-bourbonnensis", "centerNodeType": "taxonomy", "generatedAt": "2026-05-28T16:28:22", "includedNodeCount": 3, "includedLinkCount": 2, "layoutMode": "precomputed-static"}, "center": {"id": "taxonomy-species-terpsiphone-bourbonnensis", "name": "毛里求斯寿带", "type": "taxonomy"}, "nodes": [{"id": "bird-毛里求斯寿带-1e1ac4dc", "name": "毛里求斯寿带", "englishName": "Mascarene paradise flycatcher", "latinName": "Terpsiphone bourbonnensis", "type": "bird", "status": "LC", "summary": "毛里求斯寿带（台湾作馬斯卡拉林綬帶，学名：Terpsiphone bourbonnensis）是分佈在毛里裘斯及留尼旺的壽帶屬。是鹟科寿带鸟属鸟类，包含留尼汪亚种（T. b. desolata）和毛里求斯亚种2个亚种。体长15-20厘米，缺乏大多数寿带鸟常见的长中央尾羽。雄鸟头部黑色，胸部具灰色领环，上体深栗色，翅棕褐色，下体浅灰色，虹膜黑色具蓝色眼圈，脚爪铁灰色；雌鸟头部暗灰色，喙色较淡，毛里求斯亚种体型更大且羽色更鲜艳，牠們棲息在亞熱帶或熱帶低地的潮濕森林。 毛里求斯寿带体重约10.79克，翼长约70毫米，嘴峰长约15.9毫米，喙宽度约5.2毫米，喙厚度约4毫米，跗蹠长约20.4毫米，尾长约71毫米。毛里求斯寿带在其分布区内为留鸟，食性为肉食性，主要食物来源是陆生无脊椎动物。 亚种 T. b. bourbonnensis：分布于留尼汪岛。 T. b. desolata：分布于毛里求斯。 參考", "shortSummary": "毛里求斯寿带（台湾作馬斯卡拉林綬帶，学名：Terpsiphone bourbonnensis）是分佈在毛里裘斯及留尼旺的壽帶屬。是鹟科寿带鸟属鸟类，包含留尼汪亚种（T. b.", "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/52/R%C3%A9union_paradise_flycatcher_%28Terpsiphone_bourbonnensis_bourbonnensis%29_male.jpg/960px-R%C3%A9union_paradise_flycatcher_%28Terpsiphone_bourbonnensis_bourbonnensis%29_male.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-terpsiphone", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-terpsiphone-bourbonnensis", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-terpsiphone", "species": "taxonomy-species-terpsiphone-bourbonnensis"}, "expandable": true, "x": -23.97, "y": 224.18, "z": -687.53}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-terpsiphone-bourbonnensis", "name": "毛里求斯寿带", "latinName": "Terpsiphone bourbonnensis", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "毛里求斯寿带（Terpsiphone bourbonnensis）是图谱中的分